<div class="text"><p><a href="/undeclaredarts/" target="_blank">Undeclared Arts</a>&nbsp;is a gateway program that allows first year students to explore various degrees in the Faculty of Arts before selecting one that best matches their interests and goals. Students in Undeclared Arts may sample philosophy courses, and may subsequently transfer to the new BA in Philosophy, or to the&nbsp;<a href="/artsandcontemporarystudies/index.html" target="_blank">BA in Arts and Contemporary Studies</a>, or to other degree programs in the Faculty of Arts. See the&nbsp;<a href="/undeclaredarts/students/current-students/transferability-guidelines/index.html" target="_blank">Transferability Guidelines</a>.</p></div>

